Name: Epic Saeg Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Greater Saeg Rune, Level 4 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes the bond between brothers and sisters, the bond of family and clan, and supporting those you care about. Those who channel this rune are able to bolster their allies, strengthening their courage and resolve.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following features.SPACERitualistic BondSPACEYou can spend TIME1-5TIME minutes performing a ritual that binds you and up to four other creatures together for TIME2-4TIME hours. Whenever you or another bonded creatures takes damage, you or one other bonded creature can choose to reduce the damage by an amount up to twice your total number of Runic Attunement Slots, taking damage equal to the amount it was reduced by.SPACESPACECourageous StandSPACEAs an action, you can empower yourself to act as a beacon of inspiration for your allies. Choose a number of creatures you can see within DISTANCE30-45DISTANCE feet, up to your Wisdom modifier. The chosen creatures gain DAMAGE3-5DAMAGEd6 temporary hit points for TIME2-4TIME hours.SPACESPACEInspiring PresenceSPACEAs a bonus action, you magically imbue a creature of your choice with divine inspiration. The target gains DAMAGE3-5DAMAGEd6's for the next TIME2-4TIME rounds. The target may spend a d6 to add it to an attack roll, ability check, or saving throw for the duration.SPACESPACEBolstering BondSPACEAs an action, you forge a bond with a willing creature you can see within DISTANCE10-15DISTANCE feet of you for the next TIME3-5TIME rounds. While you and the chosen creature are within DISTANCE10-15DISTANCE feet of each other, you both gain temporary hit points equal to your total number of Runic Attunement Slots at the start of each of your turns and have advantage on saving throws against effects either of you can see.SPACESPACEYou may invoke this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 5 runic attunement slots. Requires Wisdom 17 or greater to attune.
